<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Contact</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/styles.css">
    <style>
        form{
            width: 400px;
            max-width: 100%;
            padding: 20px; 
            margin: 20px auto;
        }
        input,  label{
            display: block;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 5px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        input[type='submit']{width: auto;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <% include partials/nav.ejs %>
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Deleniti illo enim temporibus illum harum officia, vel quod quos doloremque perferendis nobis, perspiciatis maiores ratione ipsa nisi sit distinctio porro iusto.</p>
    <p><%= qs.person%></p>
    <form id="contact-form" method="POST" action="/contact">
        <label for="who">Who do you want to contact</label>
        <input type="text" name="who" value="<%= qs.person %>">
        <label for="departament">Which departament?</label>
        <input type="text" name="departament" value="<%= qs.dept %>">
        <label for="email">Your email</label>
        <input type="email" name="email">
